 great presentation and narration;
-Cutscenes presented in a comic/handrawn style gives the game a unique personality and visual style;
-Really great shooting mechanics;
-Tense Duels;
-Excellent visuals and audio;
-Real Wild West Lawmen and outlaws in the story;
-Highly replayable story mode;
-It's price;

The Bad

-Story mode may feel a little short to some;
-Levels are linear
